1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENEH7tu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENEH7tu.jpg&h=d0541c79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"caca0a1a2178caa674a477d745f74a73f5d41f94","tid":2294232,"uid":154373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:18:15.000Z","msg":"班弱智笑鳩完日本未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0a9659eb3a45fa4f1a9a6dc5b5305848cdc0ae","tid":2294232,"uid":154373,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c2a421efe6db2736c9df322b2d444821d4ea2b65","tid":2294232,"uid":35820,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:02:58.000Z","msg":"包尾竟然唔係日本？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:18:50.000Z","msg":"弱智完未"},{"pid":"c46fc253b75849257c1b7351050e62f436da2bb6","tid":2294232,"uid":8880,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"dd2ad48aaeda070a34a96ef7643a265e3dbda2f2","tid":2294232,"uid":339228,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:04:00.000Z","msg":"呢個研究囉令到更加多嘅香港人，更加想移民"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"點會?<br />\n<br />\n香港人點先肯移民 - 最完整分析<br />\n<br />\n1. 要大幅加人工<br />\n2. 要低稅過香港<br />\n3. 要保證一家大細,阿爸,阿媽,老婆,仔女,鄰居,同學,朋友, 全部無條件移民<br />\n4. 要同當地人福利體齊<br />\n5. 要有足夠錢係完全唔做野情況下生活5年以上<br />\n6. 要一移民就馬上置業<br />\n7. 要到當地維持香港生活模式<br />\n8. 要物價低過或同香港相約<br />\n9. 要大家移去同一個地區<br />\n10. 要當地人唔准歧視自己<br />\n11. 要識講流利英文同當地語言同方言<br />\n12. 要有專業技能, 如律師, 醫生等<br />\n13. 要住大城市<br />\n14. 要交通方便過香港<br />\n15. 要可以方便隨時來往香港<br />\n16. 要一落地就成為公民, 唔需要住 N 年或讀書等條件<br />\n17. 要有香港既食物選擇<br />\n18. 要附近冇其他國家新移民<br />\n19. 要當地一個中國人都冇<br />\n20. 要當地香港人全部都係黃絲<br />\n21. 要做非藍領既工作, 餐廳超市等一律唔做<br />\n22. 要上網快過香港<br />\n23. 要全家都同意移民先可以移民<br />\n24. 要至少有1000萬財產或本身有樓可賣<br />\n25. 要做太空人係香港繼續返工同時, 該國唔可以收稅, 又繼續畀戶籍你<br />\n26. 要返工唔可以辛苦過香港<br />\n27. 要娛樂多過香港<br />\n28. 要機場航班多過香港<br />\n29. 要方便去日本旅行<br />\n30. 要所有手足離港先走，共同進退<br />\n31. 要黃店一齊搬去外國<br />\n32. 要等兩老百年歸老咗先<br />\n33. 要等大灣區發展，賺多N年夠錢退休先<br />\n34. 要讀埋個Master先<br />\n35. 要等到升埋職做CEO<br />\n36. 要供埋層樓先，仲有份基金同埋保險<br />\n37. 要冬天天氣似香港，唔可以凍到0度<br />\n38. 要夏天天氣似香港，唔可以熱過35度<br />\n39. 要四季分明，當地天氣似日本"},{"pid":"5b62673c0f5ce876ac119d609b2f66ee2bf1ec62","tid":2294232,"uid":222336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:27:28.000Z","msg":"Work-life Integration <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e692b02bf330814c09611a7c827c14cac5617e0","tid":2294232,"uid":83102,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"758b3d0f6b3dbba2a42b750a4d797187771cabc9","tid":2294232,"uid":8170,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T01:52:20.000Z","msg":"實情係歐洲啲員工懶到咩咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:32:19.000Z","msg":"死奴隸<br />\n咁勤力做乜鳩？有獎？"},{"pid":"3136fb248cf3f76094315d5d89396b23b0ac728a","tid":2294232,"uid":192589,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4a4af781bd4c3026fdbd07613ee77c220321515f","tid":2294232,"uid":7147,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T00:48:00.000Z","msg":"我一個禮拜番66個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:36:54.000Z","msg":"Lollicin"},{"pid":"6dc5363fc90a6a19ace71a0bd7a6a746163ff062","tid":2294232,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T02:37:02.000Z","msg":"香港人奴性咁強，係噉㗎啦。"},{"pid":"ff42318d4bfe51c462f164add5972fa9737b745b","tid":2294232